           move      04                   to   v-car                  .
           move      zero                 to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "9B"                 to   v-edm                  .
           move      06                   to   v-lin                  .
           move      25                   to   v-pos                  .
