      *    *                         bene nell'ultimo trimestre        *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-vnb-pre-000.
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "V"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      11                   to   v-car                  .
           move      c-dec                to   v-dec                  .
           add       02                   to   v-dec                  .
           move      spaces               to   v-sgn                  .
           move      "GD"                 to   v-edm                  .
           move      11                   to   v-lin                  .
           add       w-tes-ctr-pre        to   v-lin                  .
           move      49                   to   v-pos                  .
