      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test se campo da accettare                  *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-tes-vnb-pre
                    (1, w-tes-ctr-pre)    =    zero
