      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       vis-fdr-pre-000.
           move      "DS"                 to   v-ope                  .
           move      "A"                  to   v-tip                  .
           move      01                   to   v-car                  .
           move      11                   to   v-lin                  .
           add       w-tes-ctr-pre        to   v-lin                  .
