      *    * Normalizzazione dati non chiave testata                   *
      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       nor-nok-tes-000.
           move      zero                 to   w-tes-vnb-gea (1)      .
           move      spaces               to   w-tes-fdr-gea (1)      .
       nor-nok-tes-200.
           move      zero                 to   w-tes-ctr-pre          .
       nor-nok-tes-220.
           add       1                    to   w-tes-ctr-pre          .
           if        w-tes-ctr-pre        >    10
                     go to nor-nok-tes-999.
